aces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0693cabf0679ad948e7561281a8674bbe63ca13","tid":1961261,"uid":247019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"香港地有咩人唔係？"},{"pid":"9770e83975eee629a895793ecee6d901cafbd750","tid":1961261,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"430c8bc0c824bc4a33244e098d696da6f7d56362","tid":1961261,"uid":7436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"dream job係想揾一份人工高，番工近，工時短，冇野做既工，但真係好難揾...<br />\n未揾到不過未放棄，希望比我揾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"冇嘢做呢個要求有啲過份喎，準時放工ok?"},{"pid":"21aa978e38ded6e0da42175385e1cb8feb46e278","tid":1961261,"uid":118127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:39:26.000Z","msg":"工程都係.."},{"pid":"98149642128f05ac2ee5b1ab0588bb78b52cfb1e","tid":1961261,"uid":5301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410cd201b6f585c01dbe777f4c65b519eef9d751","tid":1961261,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實香港大部分人應該都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多grad完做頭兩年 俾你做兩三年搵唔到錢 儲極都未夠首期 好快就會跳"},{"pid":"e83aa52c9441e479056297050a9610fc7df15c29","tid":1961261,"uid":346825,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"09f1e49708f8ebaa95cb3748e37b9e14a54e6546","tid":1961261,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9e764d459424998fbc5664660f9284351e92756","tid":1961261,"uid":346825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"agger，好多職業都表面、甚至乎內涵都好光鮮，但係去到現實不論你聽返或親身做過，就大把潛規則同掣肘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我望落個搵工網，真係覺得冇份工揀得落，行行都唔啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"例如重有咩職業？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:46:07.000Z","msg":"唔賺錢嘅有各種designer、文化藝術工作者、出版、環保、科研、飲食等等。<br />\n搵到錢嘅，醫護、工程做到你死；打政府工嘅本身就身處一個困身嘅體制；做律師講就講法治精神，現實係為有錢人服務，走法律罅，一唔係你咪做義務律師咁冇咩錢收囉；學術界唔知算搵到定搵唔到錢，但係肯定都有小圈子同埋入左去又好困身。<br />\n<br />\n幾乎份份工都會咁。我諗簡單黎講，係因為香港果種做死人、人食人、賺到盡嘅工作文化搞到咁。不過都可能我睇得負面，雞蛋裏挑骨頭啦。<br />\n<br />\ndream job呢樣野都係流於理想同睇落光鮮亮麗，做落就唔同架喇。"},{"pid":"c7429c97d4e790b12376154d1b57e6deadd318ca","tid":1961261,"uid":239316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410cd201b6f585c01dbe777f4c65b519eef9d751","tid":1961261,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實香港大部分人應該都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多grad完做頭兩年 俾你做兩三年搵唔到錢 儲極都未夠首期 好快就會跳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"可以曾經為份dream job奮鬥過努力過<br />\n就算只係做fg頭幾年都好心滿意足<br />\n香港地點都要為生活同現實低頭<br />\n唔通份dream job八千一個月做成世咩<br />\n更何況好多行業K型 就當你唔計較錢<br />\n做六七年都晉升唔到一定會心灰意冷轉行"},{"pid":"25fa4c97e6ab62efc8c7eb111be57386c75523f1","tid":1961261,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:06:38.000Z","msg":"暫時係咪得牙醫、職治、物治相對正常？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"